snippet.title: SHANSHUI 山水  Game teaser
snippet.description:
Shanshui is a 10min VR fishing game aiming to relax the player. Immerse yourself in a Chinese landscape painting and catch mythical fishes!

This game was made in 2 months by a team of 5 as a student project for the ENJMIN school. 

Get the game for free on Itch.io!
https://giomee.itch.io/shanshui
